"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-world-relays-athletics-2024-track-and-field\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The World Athletics Relays competition, which determines the bulk of the Paris Olympic 4x100m and 4x400m fields, airs live on NBC Sports andPeacockon Saturday and Sunday from the Bahamas.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2017_World_Championships_in_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.999999914280128, \"rank\": 8.57198790504374e-08, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2017_World_Championships_in_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2017_World_Championships_in_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9880500362643135, \"rank\": 0.012018919477772262, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 0.9999787758612445, \"rank\": 1.9937101030614216e-05, \"text\": \"Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Relays air live Saturday at 7:05 p.m.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET onPeacockand Sunday at 7 p.m.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET on CNBC, NBCSports.com, the NBC Sports app andPeacock.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9863951442063666, \"rank\": 0.013790343250492984, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCSports.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9880500362643135, \"rank\": 0.012018919477772262, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top 14 nations in each relay - men's and women's 4x100m and 4x400m, plus the mixed-gender 4x400m - qualify for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The nations that qualify do not have to use the same runners at the Olympics as they use at World Relays.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Saturday, the top two nations in each first-round heat for every relay qualify for the Olympics and advance to Sunday's finals, where results determine lane draws for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also Sunday, a repechage round for nations that did not advance to finals will be held.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two nations in each repechage heat also qualify for Paris.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997021705428, \"rank\": 2.978295707947958e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last two nations to qualify for each Olympic relay will be determined by world rankings on June 30.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. team for World Relays is headlined by Olympic medalists Noah Lyles and Gabby Thomas.The full U.S. roster is here.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking at the entire entry list, the Bahamas stands out with reigning Olympic women's and men's 400m champions Shaunae Miller-Uibo and Steven Gardiner both in its mixed 4x400m pool.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 0.9999787758612445, \"rank\": 1.9937101030614216e-05, \"text\": \"Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}, {\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaunae_Miller-Uibo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaunae Miller-Uibo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaunae_Miller-Uibo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaunae_Miller-Uibo\"}, {\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Gardiner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steven Gardiner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Gardiner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Gardiner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last August, the U.S. swept the men's and women's 4x100m relay titles at the world championships for the first time since 2007.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1448, \"end